('vn', 47, '', 'Onkyo HT-S5405', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	H&amp;atilde;ng:&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-tab-span&quot; style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Onkyo&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	Bảo h&amp;agrave;nh:&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-tab-span&quot; style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;12 Th&amp;aacute;ng&lt;/div&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;em&gt;With packaged home theater, you want ease-of-use and maximum features for your investment. Onkyo&amp;rsquo;s HT-S5405 adds to the equation a level of A/V quality rarely seen at the entry level. In the age of Blu-ray, HDMI&amp;reg; is the king of connectors. That&amp;rsquo;s why Onkyo equipped the HT-S5405&amp;rsquo;s receiver with four of the latest HDMI inputs to handle both 3D video and pristine audio from high-definition Dolby and DTS codecs. Versatile HDMI also opens the door to an Audio Return Channel from your HDTV&amp;rsquo;s tuner to the receiver, plus on-screen display functionality for on-the-fly adjustment of settings. Meanwhile, a handy front-panel USB input lets you hook up your iPod/iPhone and send a pure digital signal to the receiver. Also on the front panel are analog A/V inputs for easy connection of a camcorder or game console. During set-up, Audyssey 2EQ&amp;reg; adjusts the soundstage to your listening space, to make the most of the 5.1-channel surround-sound speaker set. The package includes a powered subwoofer that delivers greater bass impact without taxing the receiver. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;SYSTEM CONFIGURATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	5.1-Channel Home Theater Receiver HT-R548&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	5.1-Channel Home Theater Speaker System HTP-548&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;GENERAL SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;A/V RECEIVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	160 W/Ch at 6 Ohms, 1 kHz, 1 Channel Driven, JEITA&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Frequency Response: 20 Hz&amp;ndash;50 kHz/+1 dB, -3 dB (DSP bypass)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	WHD: 435 x 150 x 328 mm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Weight: 7.6 kg&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;SPEAKER SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Front Speaker&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Max. Input Power: 120 W&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Impedance: 6 Ohms&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Frequency Response: 80 Hz&amp;ndash;20 kHz&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	WHD: 101 x 161 x 115 mm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Weight: 0.8 kg&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Center Speaker&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Max. Input Power: 120 W&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Impedance: 6 Ohms&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Frequency Response: 80 Hz&amp;ndash;20 kHz&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	WHD: 230 x 103 x 115 mm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Weight: 1.3 kg&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Surround Speaker&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Max. Input Power: 120 W&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Impedance: 6 Ohms&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Frequency Response: 80 Hz&amp;ndash;20 kHz&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	WHD: 101 x 161 x 115 mm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Weight: 0.7 kg&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Subwoofer&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Rated Output Power: 80 W (IEC)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Frequency Response: 27 Hz&amp;ndash;150 Hz&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	WHD: 211 x 425 x 391 mm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Weight: 8.1 kg&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;A/V RECEIVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	5.1-Channel Home Theater Receiver HT-R548&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	HDMI&amp;reg; Support for 3D, Audio Return Channel, Deep Color&amp;trade;, x.v.Color&amp;trade;, LipSync, Dolby&amp;reg; TrueHD, DTS-HD Master Audio&amp;trade;, DVD-Audio, Super Audio CD, Multichannel PCM, and CEC&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	4 HDMI Inputs and 1 Output&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Direct Digital Connection of iPod/iPhone via Front-Panel USB Port&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Dolby&amp;reg; TrueHD, DTS-HD Master Audio&amp;trade;, Dolby&amp;reg; Digital Plus, DTS-HD High-Resolution Audio&amp;trade; Decoding&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	TI Burr-Brown 192 kHz/24-Bit DACs for All Channels&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	PLL (Phase Locked Loop) Jitter-Cleaning Circuit Technology for S/PDIF Audio&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Audyssey 2EQ&amp;reg; for Room Acoustic Correction&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Audyssey Dynamic EQ&amp;reg; for Loudness Correction&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Audyssey Dynamic Volume&amp;reg; to Maintain Optimal Listening Level and Dynamic Range&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Overlaid On-Screen Display (OSD) via HDMI&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	H.C.P.S. (High Current Power Supply) Massive High Power Transformer&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Optimum Gain Volume Circuitry&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Advanced 32-Bit Processing DSP Chip&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	4 DSP Modes for Gaming: Rock, Sports, Action, and RPG&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	EX.Bass for Deeper, More Dynamic Bass&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Advanced Music Optimizer for Compressed Digital Music Files&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Theater-Dimensional Virtual Surround Function&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	CinemaFILTER&amp;trade;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Direct Mode&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Double Bass Function&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Non-Scaling Configuration&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	A-Form Listening Mode Memory&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	HDTV-Capable (720p/1080i) Component Video Switching (2 Inputs and 1 Output)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	5 Composite Video Inputs (1 Front/4 Rear) and 2 Outputs&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	3 Digital Audio Inputs (2 Optical and 1 Coaxial)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	6 Analog Audio Inputs (1 Front/5 Rear) and 1 Output&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Subwoofer Pre Out&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Speaker A/B Terminals&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Color-Coded Speaker Terminals&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Headphone Jack&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Crossover Adjustment (40/50/60/70/80/90/100/120/150/200 Hz)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	A/V Sync Control (Up to 400 ms at 48 kHz)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Tone Control (Bass/Treble) for Front L/R Channels&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	3-Mode Display Dimmer (Normal/Dim/Dimmer)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	40 FM/AM Random Presets&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	RIHD (Remote Interactive over HDMI) for System Control&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Compatible with RI (Remote Interactive) Dock for iPod/iPhone&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Full-Function RI Remote Control&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;SPEAKER SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	8 cm Cone (Front/Surround Speakers)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	8 cm Cone x 2 (Center Speaker)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	16 cm Cone (Subwoofer)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Gloss Finished (Front/Center/Surround/Subwoofer Speakers)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Magnetically Shielded (Front/Center Speakers)&lt;/p&gt;', '', ''),
('vn', 48, '', 'Onkyo HT-S9300 7.1', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	H&amp;atilde;ng:&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-tab-span&quot; style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Onkyo&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	Bảo h&amp;agrave;nh:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-tab-span&quot; style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;12 Th&amp;aacute;ng&lt;/div&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Cast aside your preconceptions of packaged home theater. The HT-S9305THX and HT-S9300THX receiver/speaker systems offer a rare combination of all-in-one convenience and THX quality assurance. With Onkyo, you can take it for granted that you&amp;rsquo;ll be getting a smart amalgam of the latest processing and connectivity features. But what really sets these systems apart from your standard HTiB is the sheer quality of the speakers. All five of the HT-S9305THX&amp;rsquo;s front, center, and surround speakers feature woofer diaphragms made with Onkyo&amp;rsquo;s advanced A-OMF material. The same goes for the HT-S9300THX&amp;rsquo;s seven-speaker set, which adds surround back speakers to the equation. Driving each system is an A/V receiver that brings together a hand-picked selection of today&amp;rsquo;s most vital home entertainment technologies. Burr-Brown audio DACs work alongside PLL jitter-cleaning circuitry to get the best out of lossless Dolby and DTS formats, as well as the expanded height channels of Dolby&amp;reg; Pro Logic&amp;reg; IIz. Meanwhile, HDMI&amp;reg; 1.4a brings 3D video compatibility, and Faroudja DCDi Cinema&amp;trade; enables 1080p upscaling via HDMI of all video sources. Among the other highlights of these impressive systems are powered Zone 2 audio and Audyssey room-correction.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; SYSTEM CONFIGURATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	7.1-Channel Home Theater Receiver HT-R980&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	7.1-Channel Home Theater Speaker System&amp;nbsp;HTP-980&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; GENERAL SPECIFICATIONS A/V RECEIVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	130 W/Ch at 6 Ohms, 1 kHz, 1 Channel Driven, IEC Frequency Response: 5 Hz&amp;ndash;100 kHz/+1 dB, -3 dB (DSP bypass) WHD: 435 x 151.5 x 328.5 mm Weight: 9.6 kg&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;SPEAKER SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Front Speaker Max. Input Power: 130 W Impedance: 8 Ohms Frequency Response: 50 Hz&amp;ndash;45 kHz WHD: 158 x 433 x 199 mm Weight: 5.3 kg Center Speaker Max. Input Power: 130 W Impedance: 8 Ohms Frequency Response: 50 Hz&amp;ndash;45 kHz WHD: 433 x 158 x 199 mm Weight: 5.3 kg Surround Speaker Max. Input Power: 130 W Impedance: 8 Ohms Frequency Response: 50 Hz&amp;ndash;45 kHz WHD: 200 x 275 x 169 mm Weight: 3.5 kg Surround Back Speaker (HT-S9300THX Only) Max. Input Power: 130 W Impedance: 8 Ohms Frequency Response: 50 Hz&amp;ndash;45 kHz WHD: 200 x 275 x 169 mm Weight: 3.5 kg Subwoofer Rated Output Power: 125 W Minimum Continuous Power (6 Ohms, 100 Hz, Maximum 1% THD) Frequency Response: 20 Hz&amp;ndash;100 Hz WHD: 380 x 444 x 429 mm Weight: 15.5 kg &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES A/V RECEIVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	THX&amp;reg; I/S Plus&amp;trade; Certified THX&amp;reg; Loudness Plus&amp;trade;, THX&amp;reg; Surround EX&amp;trade;, and THX Listening Modes (Movies, Music, Games) HDMI&amp;reg; (Version 1.4a to Support 3D and Audio Return Channel) with Deep Color&amp;trade;, x.v.Color&amp;trade;, LipSync, Dolby&amp;reg; TrueHD, DTS-HD Master Audio&amp;trade;, DVD-Audio, Super Audio CD, Multichannel PCM, and CEC Audio and 1080p Video Processing via HDMI (4 Inputs and 1 Output) Dolby&amp;reg; TrueHD, DTS-HD Master Audio&amp;trade;, Dolby&amp;reg; Digital Plus, DTS-HD High-Resolution Audio&amp;trade; Decoding HDMI Video Upscaling to 1080p with Faroudja DCDi Cinema&amp;trade; Dolby&amp;reg; Pro Logic&amp;reg; IIz for New Surround Channels Burr-Brown 192 kHz/24-Bit DACs (PCM1690) for All Channels Three-Stage Inverted Darlington Circuitry PLL Jitter-Cleaning Circuit Technology Audyssey 2EQ&amp;reg; for Room Acoustic Correction Audyssey Dynamic EQ&amp;reg; for Loudness Correction Audyssey Dynamic Volume&amp;reg; Powered Zone 2 and Zone 2 Line-Out for Playback of Separate Source in Another Room Overlaid Graphical On-Screen Display (OSD) via HDMI WRAT (Wide Range Amplifier Technology) H.C.P.S. (High Current Power Supply) Massive High-Power Transformer Linear Optimum Gain Volume Circuitry Advanced 32-Bit Processing DSP Chip 4 DSP Modes for Gaming: Rock, Sports, Action, and RPG (Role Playing Game) Music Optimizer&amp;trade; for Compressed Digital Music Files Direct Mode Non-Scaling Configuration A-Form Listening Mode Memory Theater-Dimensional Virtual Surround Function Universal Port for Single-Cable Connection of Optional Onkyo Dock for iPhone/iPod or DAB+ Radio Tuner HDTV-Capable (720p/1080i) Component Video Switching (2 Inputs and 1 Output) Front-Panel Audio Input for Portable Devices Front-Panel Auxiliary A/V Input 4 Digital Inputs (2 Optical and 2 Coaxial) 4 A/V Inputs and 1 Output Video Output (Monitor) 1 Audio Input Subwoofer Pre Out Color-Coded, Banana Plug-Compatible Speaker Posts (Except Front High or Zone 2) A/V Sync Control Function (Up to 200 ms in 10 ms Steps) 40 FM/AM Random Presets RDS (PS/RT/PTY/TP) RIHD (Remote Interactive over HDMI) for System Control Compatible with RI (Remote Interactive) Dock for iPod Preprogrammed RI Remote Control&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;SPEAKER SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	12 cm A-OMF Diaphragm Woofer x 2 (Front/Center Speakers) 2.5 cm Soft-Dome Tweeter (Front/Center Speakers) 13 cm A-OMF Diaphragm Woofer (Surround/Surround Back Speakers) 2.5 cm Soft-Dome Tweeter (Surround/Surround Back Speakers) 30 cm Cone (Subwoofer) Magnetically Shielded (Front/Center Speakers Only)&