('vn', 55, '', 'VSX-1020-K', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	H&amp;atilde;ng: &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Pioneer&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	Bảo h&amp;agrave;nh: 12 th&amp;aacute;ng&lt;/div&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	T&amp;iacute;nh năng đặc biệt (special features):&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	* 7.1 channel, 110w x 7ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	~ 9.1ch: 2 front, 2 front height / or 2 front wide or 2 B speaker, 1 center, 2 surround, 2 surround back).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;* Dolby TrueHD and DTS-HD Master Audio Decoders&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	** HDMI&amp;reg; V.1.4a with 3D - Hỗ trợ h&amp;igrave;nh ảnh 3-D. 6 Inputs / 1 Output&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	* MCAAC: tự động c&amp;acirc;n chỉnh loa.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	* Works with iPhone Certified - includes USB/Composite Video Cable, Free iControl AVR iPhone App&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	* Bluetooth ready with optional Pioneer AS-BT100 Bluetooth Adapter&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	* Anchor Bay&amp;reg; Video Processing: n&amp;acirc;ng cao h&amp;igrave;nh ảnh gốc.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	------------------&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATION:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Amplification:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Power in: 245w /60Hz.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Power out: 110w x 7ch, 80w + 80wz (20Hz&amp;ndash; 20kHz, 8 ohm).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Audio features:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	192 kHz / 24-bit DAC.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;Dolby TrueHD.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Dolby prologic IIz.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Dolby digital / EX.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Dolby digital plus&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;DTS-HD Master audio.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	DTS 96/24.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	DTS neo 6.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	DTS express.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Multi PCM playback (192kHz) via HDMI.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	SACD playback via HDMI (2 ch).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Advanced surround.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Midnight Listening.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Advanced sound retriever technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Acoustic Calibration.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Built-in microphone.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	PQLS: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.pioneerelectronics.com/PUSA/Products/HomeEntertainment/AV-Receivers/Enhanced+Content/Receivers/Performance/Jitter&quot;&gt;http://www.pioneerelectronics.com/PUSA/Products/HomeEntertainment/AV-Receivers/Enhanced+Content/Receivers/Performance/Jitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Video features:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	HDMI (v1.4 with 3-D).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Deep color and x.v.color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	PureCinema video processing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Anchor Bay&amp;reg; Video Processing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Convenience:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	30 tuner presets.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Sleep timer 30-60-90 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Conectivities:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	6 HDMI in, 1 HDMI out.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	4 digital input (2 coaxial, 2 optical).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Bluetooth port compatible with optional Pioneer AS-BT100 bluetooth adapter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	IPhone compatible.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Preout: 0.1 preout (subwoofer preout).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Radio:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	AM/FM - Digital.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Tuner Frequency Range: AM: 530-1700 kHz, FM: 87.5-108 MHz.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Antenna Form Factor Loop AM.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	-----------------&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Link tham khảo:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.pioneerelectronics.com/PUSA/Products/HomeEntertainment/AV-Receivers/PioneerReceivers/ci.VSX-1020-K.Kuro&quot;&gt;http://www.pioneerelectronics.com/PUSA/ ... 020-K.Kuro&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Manual (pdf):&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.pioneerelectronics.com/StaticFiles/Manuals/Home/VSX-1020_OperatingInstructions0302.pdf&quot;&gt;http://www.pioneerelectronics.com/Stati ... ns0302.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Back image:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/vsx-1020_rear_callouts.jpg&quot;&gt;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G ... llouts.jpg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', ''),
